<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Report Card Available</title></head>
<body style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px">
  <h2 style="color:#059669">Report Card Available</h2>
  <p>Dear Parent/Guardian,</p>
  <p>The report card for <strong>{{studentName}}</strong> ({{term}}) is now available.</p>
  <a href="{{reportUrl}}" style="background:#059669;color:#fff;padding:10px 20px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px">View Report Card</a>
  <p style="margin-top:20px;color:#6b7280;font-size:12px">{{schoolName}}</p>
</body>
</html>
